  Dependencies
    File::Spec::Functions
    Module::Build
    ExtUtils::CBuilder

  Installation
    This distribution requires a functioning C++ compiler and (to make life
    easy) a version of make.

    The distribution is based on Module::Build and ExtUtils::CBuilder, so
    use the following procedure:

      perl Build.PL
      ./Build
      ./Build test
      ./Build install

